{"tid":1104703,"cid":15,"subCid":0,"title":"岡拉克：美股仍處熊市 料夏季尾將再度下跌","createTime":"2019-04-13T10:22:16.000Z","updateTime":"2019-04-14T16:54:22.000Z","uid":66271,"like":0,"dislike":8,"uniUserReply":10,"replies":[{"pid":"b36e53447bd692989d45352c62ad50cae568495a","tid":1104703,"uid":66271,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-13T10:22:16.000Z","msg":"「新債王」岡拉克(Jeff Gundlach)接受瑞士金融媒體The Market訪問時表示，美股仍然處於熊市，料在夏季尾將再度轉為負收益。他預料，2020年美國總統大選期間，局勢可能要遠遠糟於2016年，甚至可能會出現暴力騷亂事件。<br />\n<br />\n岡拉克指出，比較典型的是，熊市起點通常會有一個明顯的下行趨勢，再出現一次幾乎是完全的反彈，而這其實是一個很好的賣出機會。<br />\n<br />\n岡拉克認為，目前並無足夠證據顯示股市蓬勃，他認為股市只是動盪，而動盪也是整體金融市場的普遍現象。唯一真正發生了的變化是經濟在放緩，石油價格上升。"},{"pid":"8ba36cf483edf5667b622d9f585968e851a6dc1e","tid":1104703,"uid":84081,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-13T10:24:18.000Z","msg":"負面因素正逐步發酵<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6d8846e21af84644f5a78ac9e9c46b3984660c28","tid":1104703,"uid":198008,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-13T11:53:52.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/1aazpsw.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F1aazpsw.png&h=fb17d2ce&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"1a2904e2a5a2e755d4cd8c52f2f303ec7d31cf34","tid":1104703,"uid":51920,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-13T12:51:49.000Z","msg":"睇錯阿拉岡"},{"pid":"10d57cd93add9c15dc2bfc8701e39b65805f5d59","tid":1104703,"uid":44980,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-04-13T13:42:28.000Z","msg":"佢好堅真大師級<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/scare.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/scare.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/scare.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n都要睇下走唔走左先<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3a8854d8b5d7bdd7276edaa509521d9d496bc0a4","tid":1104703,"uid":166288,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-04-13T14:20:43